'''辛賈爾'''（{{Lang-ar|Sinjar}}，{{Lang-ar|سنجار}}，''Sinjar''；{{Lang-la|Singara}}），也稱作'''辛葛'''（Shingal, Central Kurdish:<span> </span><span lang="ckb">شەنگال</span>, Shengali: ''Şengal''; {{Lang-syc|ܫܝܓܳܪ}}, ''Shiggor''），從前則是被稱作'''珊賈爾（Sanjár）'''<ref name="abul">{{Citation|last = Abul Fazl-i-Ạllámí|others = Translated by H.S. Jarrett|ref = {{harvid|Jarrett|1894}}|title = The Áin I Akbarí|publisher = Baptist Mission Press for the Asiatic Society of Bengal|location = Calcutta|volume = Vol. III|url = https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=81AmAQAAIAAJ&pg=PA26|contribution = Description of the Earth|p = 25–27|date = 1894}}</ref>。 辛賈爾位於伊拉克[[尼尼微省|尼尼微省]]，是{{link-en|辛賈爾縣|Sinjar District}}的一座城鎮，位於{{link-en|辛賈爾山脈|Sinjar Mountains}}旁邊。2013年的人口88,023人<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.world-gazetteer.com/wg.php?x=1&men=gcis&lng=en&des=gamelan&geo=-3&col=abcdefghinoq&msz=1500&geo=-105|title = Iraq: largest cities and towns and statistics of their population|publisher = World Gazetteer <!-- Blacklisted but valid: |archiveurl=http://archive[dot]today/xrUEM#selection-115.0-115.15 |archivedate=27 June 2013 |accessdate=20 June 2014 -->}}</ref> 。
{{link-en|辛賈爾山|Sinjar Mountains}}山頂有一座重要的奇美拉神寺。

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Singara.jpg|left]]在公元二世紀，辛賈爾成為羅馬帝國的軍事基地，直至於360年被薩珊王朝攻陷。六世紀初，一個名為Qadišaiē (Kαδίσηυοι)的部落定居於此。其後，阿拉伯穆斯林在Iyad ibn Ganan的帶領下征服此地<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Byzantine Apocalyptic Tradition|url=https://archive.org/details/byzantineapocaly00alex|last=Alexander|first=Paul J|publisher=University of California Press|year=1985|isbn=0520049985|location=|pages=[https://archive.org/details/byzantineapocaly00alex/page/n93 27]}}</ref>。[[File:Al-Jazira.svg|thumb]]

羅馬地理學者熟知的{{link-en|普丁格地圖|Peutinger's map}}將辛賈爾繪於[[波斯|波斯]]領土西部，{{link-en|辛賈爾山脈|Sinjar Mountains}}周圍的區域。對中世紀的阿拉伯人而言，辛賈爾是拉比亞省（Diyār Rabīʿa）的一部分，居住著拉比亞部落（Rabīʿa" tribe）。附近的珊賈爾平原(現稱為{{link-en|尼尼微平原|Nineveh plains}})，是[[花拉子模|花拉子模]]以及[[哈里發國|哈里發國]][[阿布·阿拔斯·阿卜杜拉·马蒙·本·哈伦|阿布·阿拔斯·阿卜杜拉·马蒙·本·哈伦]]在位時天文學家的觀測台所在。<ref name="abul">{{Citation|last = Abul Fazl-i-Ạllámí|others = Translated by H.S. Jarrett|ref = {{harvid|Jarrett|1894}}|title = The Áin I Akbarí|publisher = Baptist Mission Press for the Asiatic Society of Bengal|location = Calcutta|volume = Vol. III|url = https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=81AmAQAAIAAJ&pg=PA26|contribution = Description of the Earth|p = 25–27|date = 1894}}</ref>這座城市也以擁有一間8世紀[[東方亞述教會|東方亞述教會]]教堂聞名。<ref>{{Cite book|url = http://books.google.com/books?id=8CYpAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA126|title = A short history of Syriac literature|publisher = |accessdate = 23 December 2014}}</ref>

== 近況 ==
2007年，伊拉克[[蓋達組織|蓋達組織]]策畫的幾起爆炸案殺害了數百名辛賈爾[[雅兹迪|雅兹迪]]人。<ref>{{Cite news|last1 = Shefler|first1 = Gil|title = Islamic State accused of capturing Yazidi women and forcing them to convert, or else|url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/national/religion/islamic-state-accused-of-capturing-yazidi-women-and-forcing-them-to-convert-or-else/2014/08/07/5e6080ba-1e70-11e4-9b6c-12e30cbe86a3_story.html|accessdate = October 7, 2014|work = Washington Post|agency = Religion News Service|date = August 7, 2014}}</ref>

2014年8月，在[[佩什梅格|庫德自由鬥士]]被擊退之後，[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]佔據了辛賈爾地區，並且製造了[[辛賈爾大屠殺|辛賈爾大屠殺]]。根據8月5日和8月6日的雅茲迪目擊者，伊斯蘭國殺害了500-2,000名雅茲迪平民，使得這些被伊斯蘭國稱為"魔鬼崇拜者"的雅茲迪居民開始大規模逃亡。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/islamic-state-seize-town-of-sinjar-pushing-out-kurds-and-sending-yazidis-fleeing/2014/08/03/52ab53f1-48de-4ae1-9e1d-e241a15f580e_story.html|title = Islamic State seizes town of Sinjar, pushing out Kurds and sending Yazidis fleeing|author = Loveday Morris|work = [[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|publisher = WP website|date = 3 August 2014|accessdate = 7 August 2014}}</ref> [[纽约时报|纽约时报]]在8月7日報導，"伊斯蘭國處決了數十名雅茲迪男子，將他們的妻子給予未婚的[[聖戰士|聖戰士]]。"<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/08/world/middleeast/isis-forces-in-iraq.html?_r=0, Jihadists Rout Kurds in North and Seize Strategic Iraqi Dam]. </ref>

2014年12月20日晚間，庫德族部隊在第一次大規模攻勢將結束時進入了辛賈爾<ref name="45_execution">{{Cite web|url = http://www.dpa-international.com/news/international/iraqs-kurds-press-offensive-against-islamic-state-in-sinjar-a-43622773.html?|title = Iraq's Kurds press offensive against Islamic State in Sinjar|work = DPA International|accessdate = 21 December 2014}}</ref>，但是一直無法取得完全控制，辛賈爾城南仍有[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]的抵抗。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.wsj.com/articles/iraqi-kurds-push-into-sinjar-after-islamic-state-occupation-1419165717|title = Iraqi Kurds Advance Against Islamic State in Sinjar|work = Wall Street Journal|accessdate = 21 December 2014}}</ref>

2015年11月13日，在發動了第二次大規模攻勢的一日後，庫爾德族部隊和雅茲迪民兵在美軍的空中支援下，再一次進入並從伊斯蘭國手上取得對辛賈爾的完全控制<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/34806556|title=Iraqi town of Sinjar 'liberated' from IS|date=2015-11-13|newspaper=BBC News|accessdate=2018-03-11|language=en-GB}}</ref>。

